-- Angel Broking May Sell Stake for 3 Billion Rupees, Economic Times Reports
-- Thomas Abraham
-- 2010-07-27T01:50:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-27/angel-broking-may-sell-stake-for-3-billion-rupees-economic-times-reports.html

          
          
             Angel Broking Ltd., an Indian
stockbroker, is in talks with private equity investors including
General Atlantic LLC, Blackstone Group LP and Advent
International Corp. to sell a stake for 3 billion rupees ($64
million), the Economic Times reported, without saying where it
got the information.  
